# TechMate AI — IT Study Chatbot

A web-based AI study assistant built for IT students covering 4 specialised streams.

## Streams
- 🌐 Network Management
- 💻 Software Development
- 🔐 Cybersecurity
- ☁️ Cloud Computing

## Features
- AI-powered chat tutor for each stream
- Quiz engine with 3 difficulty levels (Easy, Medium, Hard)
- XP and scoring system
- Study resources per stream
- Project roadmap

 Tech Stack
- Frontend: HTML, CSS, JavaScript
- Backend: Python, Flask
- AI Model: LLaMA 3.3 70B via Groq API

 How to Run
1. Clone the repository
2. Install dependencies:
   pip install flask flask-cors groq python-dotenv
3. Create a .env file and add your Groq API key:
   GROQ_API_KEY=your_key_here
4. Run the server:
   python app.py
5. Open your browser at http://127.0.0.1:5000

   Live Demo
 https://ch-at-bo-t.onrender.com

